7. Cigar:davidoff == Color:amber
8. Beverage:lemonade is in the middle
9. Nationality:german is on the far left
10. Cigar:bolivar is on the left or right of Pet:ferret
11. Cigar:davidoff is to the left or right of Pet:guinea-pig
12. Cigar:vegafina == Beverage:mirinda
13. Nationality:chinese == Cigar:montecristo
14. Nationality:german is to the left or right of Color:apricot

